DialogueNode.dialogue: Can you believe that he did that?
I feel so bad for her. If it was me... Gosh, I don't even know what I'd do.
So inconsiderate. Someone really should stop him... Maybe we should tell HR.
You can. But I for one am NOT about to get mixed up in this. I'd rather just shut up and endure it.
Maybe you're right... I don't know. Anyway, I should be getting back to work now.
Alright. I'll see you around, Dave.
